04:17.652 --> 04:20.070
I have to go. It's part of the job.

06:13.652 --> 06:15.651
Hey!

06:15.652 --> 06:17.652
You little shits!

06:28.652 --> 06:29.652
Are you hurt?

06:31.195 --> 06:32.652
Come on! Come on!

06:51.652 --> 06:55.651
You think it'd be better if
you were dead instead of her?

06:55.652 --> 06:57.651
What would that fix, Kutter?

06:57.652 --> 06:59.651
There's no shame in being alive.

06:59.652 --> 07:01.652
Fuck do you know? You weren't there.

07:01.778 --> 07:03.651
Hey.

07:03.652 --> 07:06.651
He wasn't there because he broke his arm

07:06.652 --> 07:08.652
